    },
    {
      "global_id": 5498,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 3,
      "verse_key": "74:3",
      "text_ar": "وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Thy Lord magnify,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5499,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 4,
      "verse_key": "74:4",
      "text_ar": "وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Thy raiment purify,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5500,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 5,
      "verse_key": "74:5",
      "text_ar": "وَٱلرُّجْزَ فَٱهْجُرْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Pollution shun!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5501,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 6,
      "verse_key": "74:6",
      "text_ar": "وَلَا تَمْنُن تَسْتَكْثِرُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And show not favour, seeking wordly gain!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5502,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 7,
      "verse_key": "74:7",
      "text_ar": "وَلِرَبِّكَ فَٱصْبِرْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "For the sake of thy Lord, be patient!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5503,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 8,
      "verse_key": "74:8",
      "text_ar": "فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِى ٱلنَّاقُورِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "For when the trumpet shall sound,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5504,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 9,
      "verse_key": "74:9",
      "text_ar": "فَذَٰلِكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ يَوْمٌ عَسِيرٌ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Surely that day will be a day of anguish,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5505,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 10,
      "verse_key": "74:10",
      "text_ar": "عَلَى ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ غَيْرُ يَسِيرٍ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Not of ease, for disbelievers."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5506,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 11,
      "verse_key": "74:11",
      "text_ar": "ذَرْنِى وَمَنْ خَلَقْتُ وَحِيدًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Leave Me (to deal) with him whom I created lonely,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5507,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 12,
      "verse_key": "74:12",
      "text_ar": "وَجَعَلْتُ لَهُۥ مَالًا مَّمْدُودًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And then bestowed upon him ample means,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5508,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 13,
      "verse_key": "74:13",
      "text_ar": "وَبَنِينَ شُهُودًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And sons abiding in his presence"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5509,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 14,
      "verse_key": "74:14",
      "text_ar": "وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُۥ تَمْهِيدًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And made (life) smooth for him."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5510,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 15,
      "verse_key": "74:15",
      "text_ar": "ثُمَّ يَطْمَعُ أَنْ أَزِيدَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Yet he desireth that I should give more."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5511,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 16,
      "verse_key": "74:16",
      "text_ar": "كَلَّآ ۖ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا عَنِيدًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Nay! For lo! he hath been stubborn to Our revelations."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5512,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 17,
      "verse_key": "74:17",
      "text_ar": "سَأُرْهِقُهُۥ صَعُودًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "On him I shall impose a fearful doom."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5513,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 18,
      "verse_key": "74:18",
      "text_ar": "إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "For lo! he did consider; then he planned -"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5514,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 19,
      "verse_key": "74:19",
      "text_ar": "فَقُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "(Self-)destroyed is he, how he planned!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5515,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 20,
      "verse_key": "74:20",
      "text_ar": "ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Again (self-)destroyed is he, how he planned! -"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5516,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 21,
      "verse_key": "74:21",
      "text_ar": "ثُمَّ نَظَرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Then looked he,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5517,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 22,
      "verse_key": "74:22",
      "text_ar": "ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Then frowned he and showed displeasure."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5518,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 23,
      "verse_key": "74:23",
      "text_ar": "ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ وَٱسْتَكْبَرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Then turned he away in pride"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5519,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 24,
      "verse_key": "74:24",
      "text_ar": "فَقَالَ إِنْ هَـٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحْرٌ يُؤْثَرُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And said: This is naught else than magic from of old;"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5520,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 25,
      "verse_key": "74:25",
      "text_ar": "إِنْ هَـٰذَآ إِلَّا قَوْلُ ٱلْبَشَرِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "This is naught else than speech of mortal man."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5521,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 26,
      "verse_key": "74:26",
      "text_ar": "سَأُصْلِيهِ سَقَرَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Him shall I fling unto the burning."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5522,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 27,
      "verse_key": "74:27",
      "text_ar": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا سَقَرُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "- Ah, what will convey unto thee what that burning is! -"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5523,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 28,
      "verse_key": "74:28",
      "text_ar": "لَا تُبْقِى وَلَا تَذَرُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "It leaveth naught; it spareth naught"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5524,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 29,
      "verse_key": "74:29",
      "text_ar": "لَوَّاحَةٌ لِّلْبَشَرِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "It shrivelleth the man."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5525,
      "surah": 74,
      "ayah": 30,
      "verse_key": "74:30",
      "text_ar": "عَلَيْهَا تِسْعَةَ عَشَرَ",
